The indoor-outdoor living will integrate seamlessly with wide French doors allowing patio access from three different location. As you continue your journey in the house, you will be greeted by the oversized fireplace surrounded with natural light and high ceilings. This beautiful property features a split floorplan with 3bed/2bath, all tile flooring, ceiling fans in every room, and a spacious open floor plan and oversized garage. Great room has high ceilings, can lights, fireplace, surround sound and plantation shutters.

Stunning Upscale Wood ''Schuler'' Kitchen Cabinets surround the kitchen and include a plethora of pull-out shelves, beautiful granite countertops & backsplash, recessed lighting, bar area and large center island which is great for gatherings. Newly painted

Public Remarks: This 3-bedroom/3 bath home has been completely renovated and redesigned, showcasing telltale touches of a contemporary/modern feel home with a farmhouse vibe.  NO HOA.  The home features crisp black and white paint and earthy wide plank laminate wood floors, a stylish balance of formal spaces and cozy living. Upon entering you will immediately observe the new open floor concept with floor to ceiling fireplace, vaulted ceilings, separate family room and living room areas . The gourmet kitchen features custom cabinets, waterfall counter tops and stainless appliances. The home features a spacious master bedroom with spa inspired master bath.  Additionally, one of the other two bedrooms is a en-suite with private bath. A detached Man Cave is an added bonus. A must see that won't last long.

Public Remarks: Amazing, completely updated 3 bedroom 2 bath home in great Tempe neighborhood. Conveniently close to the 101, 202, Old Town Scottsdale, ASU, Sky Harbor Airport, Tempe Town Lake and the Phoenix Zoo! Home features modern, hardwood-look porcelain tile. Beautiful upgraded quartz and backsplash in kitchen and bathrooms. Brand new white, soft-close shaker cabinets with stainless steel hardware. New stainless steel appliances. Amazing updated, spacious kitchen open to family room. Fully updated master and guest baths with modern, tiled showers and rain faucet. Updated lighting and plumbing fixtures throughout. Brand new upgraded carpet. Dual pane windows. New paint inside and out, and much more. RV gate. No HOA. New AC installed in 2022. Fabulous and luxurious Tempe home that won't last long!
